activityNotes: Very happy. First week over 20 miles. First time extending the run up the mount to 10k. Didn’t stop at all. Run up the mount was a bit slow but didn’t pause at all and created the top despite it being hard work. Lungs were good enough at the top to recover whilst jogging. Not easy though. Enjoyed the downhill stretch back to home. Legs 2 - very fresh frankly. Lungs 2-4 on the uphill only.
